# Test ROM URLs for systematic testing
# These are clean uxntal:// URLs without query parameters
# Used for testing parsing, modification, and reconstruction flows

## Special configuration syntax:
## #test_inject t^^<timeout>:emu^^{<emulator1>,<emulator2>}
## - t^^10 sets timeout to 10 seconds
## - emu^^{cuxn,buxn} tests with both cardinal-gui and buxn
## - Single # comments with test_inject apply to the next URL
## - Double ## comments are ignored
#test_inject t^^5:emu^^{cuxn,buxn,uxn}
